<createdTime>2025-02-24 08:53:45 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[Present Value (swap) shall be the sum of claims to payment of principal and interest, as discounted by a foreign exchange-specific risk-free yield curve, determined in accordance with the relevant statutory covered bond regime's rules that apply for determining sufficient coverage for the Asset pool (subject to a Covered bond programme).]]></comment>
