<createdBy>nuvolia</createdBy>
<createdTime>2025-02-24 08:53:45 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[The asset-specific value shall be the economic value of the cover pool assets, as may be described by a fair value in accordance with IFRS 13, a market value observable from executed transactions in liquid markets, or a present value that would discount future cash flows of an asset by an asset-specific interest rate curve.]]></comment>
